            text: "<p>\n\t<strong>请求帮助</strong><br />\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width: 80%;\" width=\"600\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"4\">\n\t\t\t\t用下列带有 **Could you** 的问句请求帮助。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 5%;\">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/83/72/v/108372/GE_4.1.2.3.2_1_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td valign=\"top\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 50%;\">\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>Could you </strong>do me a favor?&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t您能帮我一个忙吗？</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>https://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/83/73/v/108373/GE_4.1.2.3.2_2_v2.mp3</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td valign=\"top\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>Could you</strong> help me?</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t您能帮我吗？</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"4\">\n\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t你可以使用这些表达对他人的帮助请求表示同意。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/83/74/v/108374/GE_4.1.2.3.2_3_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td valign=\"top\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>Sure.&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t当然。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/83/75/v/108375/GE_4.1.2.3.2_4_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td valign=\"top\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>No problem.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t没问题。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/83/76/v/108376/GE_4.1.2.3.2_5_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td valign=\"top\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>OK.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t好的。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"4\">\n\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t如果你帮不了忙，你可以说 **I'm sorry, but** 来表示道歉，然后说明原因。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/83/77/v/108377/GE_4.1.2.3.2_6_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td valign=\"top\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>I&#39;m sorry, but</strong> I&#39;m really busy right now.&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t对不起，可我现在真的很忙。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/83/71/v/108371/GE_4.1.2.3.2_7_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td valign=\"top\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>I&#39;m really sorry, but</strong> I can&#39;t help you.&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t真对不起，可我帮不了你。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>",
