            text: "<p>\n\t<strong>建议活动</strong><br />\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%;\" width=\"700\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"3\">\n\t\t\t\t提出活动建议有几种方法。<br />\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"3\">\n\t\t\t\t<strong>**Let's +** 搭配动词原形</strong></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 5%;\">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/84/17/v/108417/GE_4.1.3.4.2_1_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 40%;\">\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>Let&#39;s go</strong> to the dance performance.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我们去看舞蹈演出吧。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"3\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"3\">\n\t\t\t\t<strong>**How about** 或 **what about +** 搭配动名词</strong></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 5%;\">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/84/18/v/108418/GE_4.1.3.4.2_2_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>What about meeting</strong> some friends?</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t去见一些朋友怎么样？</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"3\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"3\">\n\t\t\t\t<strong>**Could +** 搭配动词原形</strong></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/84/19/v/108419/GE_4.1.3.4.2_3_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>We <strong>could go out </strong>for a drink at Harry&#39;s Bar.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我们可以去 Harry's Bar 酒吧喝点东西。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"3\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"3\">\n\t\t\t\t<strong>**Why don't we +** 搭配动词原形</strong></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/84/16/v/108416/GE_4.1.3.4.2_4_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>Why don&#39;t we try</strong> a new restaurant?</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t我们为什不试试一家新餐馆呢？</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>",
