            text: '<p>\n\t<strong>形容词的排序</strong><br />\n\t&nbsp;</p>\n<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%;" width="650">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t当您使用一个以上的形容词进行描述时，一般的规则是把它们按大小，年龄，然后颜色的顺序排列。<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style="width: 5%;">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/91/84/v/109184/GE_4.2.1.2.1_1_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td style="width: 45%;">\n\t\t\t\t<em>That is a <strong>fat</strong>, <strong>old</strong>, <strong>black</strong> dog.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t那是一只肥肥的老黑狗。\r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t请注意这些例子中的大小-年龄-颜色的顺序：<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/91/85/v/109185/GE_4.2.1.2.1_2_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>He has <strong>big</strong>, <strong>brown</strong> eyes.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t他长着一双大大的棕色眼睛。\r\n \r\n</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/91/86/v/109186/GE_4.2.1.2.1_3_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>Her hair is <strong>shorter</strong> and <strong>grayer</strong> than before.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t她的头发比以前更短了，也变得更灰白了。 \r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/91/87/v/109187/GE_4.2.1.2.1_4_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>He&#39;s a <strong>thin</strong>, <strong>middle-aged </strong>man.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t他是个瘦瘦的中年男子。</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/91/83/v/109183/GE_4.2.1.2.1_5_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>That <strong>tall</strong>, <strong>young</strong>, <strong>blond</strong> man drives a truck.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t\t那个高个儿的，金发碧眼的年轻男子开一辆卡车。 \r\n \r\n\r\n\r\n</p>\n\t\t\t</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>',
