            text: "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%;\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"6\">\n\t\t\t\t**be** 动词的过去时否定式为 **was not** 和 **were not**，对应的缩写形式分别为 **wasn't** 和 **weren't**。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"6\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 5%;\">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/82/14/v/108214/GE_4.3.1.2.2_7_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 40%;\">\n\t\t\t\t<em>Frank <strong>was not </strong>happy in Los Angeles. &gt; Frank <strong>wasn&#39;t </strong>happy in Los Angeles.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 1%;\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 54%;\">\n\t\t\t\tFrank 以前在洛杉矶过得不开心。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 1%;\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/82/15/v/108215/GE_4.3.1.2.2_8_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\">\n\t\t\t\t<em>Oscar and Pam <strong>were not </strong>at home yesterday. &gt; Oscar and Pam <strong>weren&#39;t</strong> at home yesterday.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 1%;\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\tOscar 和 Pam 昨天不在家。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 1%;\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"6\">\n\t\t\t\t<strong>过去时疑问句</strong></td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 5%;\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 40%;\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 1%;\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 54%;\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"6\">\n\t\t\t\t在句首使用单词 **did** 来形成过去时疑问句。**did** 后使用主要动词的原形。不得在动词词尾后加 **s**。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 5%;\">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/82/16/v/108216/GE_4.3.1.2.2_9_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 40%;\">\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>Did</strong> he<strong> go </strong>to Shanghai?&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 1%;\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 54%;\">\n\t\t\t\t他去上海了吗？</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/82/17/v/108217/GE_4.3.1.2.2_10_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 40%;\">\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>Did</strong> they <strong>eat</strong> dinner?&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 1%;\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 54%;\">\n\t\t\t\t他们吃了吗？</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"6\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"6\">\n\t\t\t\t要使用 **be** 动词组成过去时疑问句，请将 **was** 或 **were** 置于问句之首。&nbsp;&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 5%;\">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/82/18/v/108218/GE_4.3.1.2.2_11_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 40%;\">\n\t\t\t\t陈述句：&nbsp; <em>He</em> <em><strong>was</strong> happy.</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 1%;\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t他以前很开心。</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 5%;\">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/82/07/v/108207/GE_4.3.1.2.2_12_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"2\" style=\"width: 40%;\">\n\t\t\t\t疑问句：&nbsp; <em><strong>Was</strong> he happy?&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 1%;\">\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 54%;\">\n\t\t\t\t他以前很开心吗？</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>",
