            text: '<div>\n\t<div>\n\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t<strong>省略形式</strong><br />\n\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%;" width="700">\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td colspan="2">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t当人们说得快速流利时，他们并不总是发出单词的每一个音。特别是元音通常会被缩短或减弱。这些弱化读音不会在标准英语中书写出。然而，重要的是能够在听到它们时识别出。<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td colspan="2">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<span id="fck_dom_range_temp_1345602520514_202">请听省略形式。注意它们书写和发音的不同之处。</span><br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%;" width="700">\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/95/64/v/109564/GE_4.4.4.3.1_11_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<em><strong>What do you</strong> think?&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/04/71/v/110471/GE_4.4.4.3.1_12_v3.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<em><strong>Where did you</strong> work?&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style="width: 5%;">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/95/65/v/109565/GE_4.4.4.3.1_13_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<em><strong>When do you</strong> study?&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/95/66/v/109566/GE_4.4.4.3.1_14_v3.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<em><strong>Why did you</strong> leave?&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/10/95/67/v/109567/GE_4.4.4.3.1_15_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<em><strong>How do you </strong>like it?&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>',
