            text: '<div>\n\t<div>\n\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t<strong>询问和介绍地点的信息</strong><br />\n\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 100%;" width="700">\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t询问他们是否喜欢自己的家乡，是鼓励他人谈论其家乡的一种方法。</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td colspan="1" rowspan="4" style="width: 5%;">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/04/82/v/110482/GE_4.6.1.4.1_1_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style="width: 47%;">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tA:<em> Where are you from?</em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t你来自哪里？</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style="width: 47%;">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tB: <em>I&#39;m from Ottawa.</em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t我来自渥太华。</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style="width: 47%;">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tA:<strong> </strong><em><strong>Do you like it there?</strong></em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t你喜欢那里吗？</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style="width: 47%;">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tB:<em> Oh, yeah. There are fantastic museums and festivals. </em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t哦，是的。那里有许多很好的博物馆和节日。</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>',
