            text: "<table border=\"0\" cellpadding=\"0\" cellspacing=\"0\" style=\"width: 100%;\" width=\"700\">\n\t<tbody>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"3\">\n\t\t\t\t表达否定意义，使用 **will + not +** 动词，缩写形式为 **won't**。<br />\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 5%;\">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/05/09/v/110509/GE_4.6.2.2.1_5_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 47%;\">\n\t\t\t\t<em>I <strong>won&#39;t get</strong> sick.&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t（我不会生病。）</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/05/10/v/110510/GE_4.6.2.2.1_6_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>They <strong>won&#39;t come</strong> with us.&nbsp;&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t（他们不会跟我们来。）</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td colspan=\"3\">\n\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t要确定时间，你可以添加表示将来的时间表达：<br />\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td style=\"width: 5%;\">\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/05/13/v/110513/GE_4.6.2.2.1_9_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em>I&#39;m going to go horseback riding <strong>on Thursday</strong>.&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t（星期四我打算去骑马。）</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/05/04/v/110504/GE_4.6.2.2.1_10_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t<em><strong>The next two days</strong> will be an adventure.&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t（接下来两天将是一场冒险。）</td>\n\t\t</tr>\n\t</tbody>\n</table>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>",
            layoutType: 'Table'
