            text: '<div>\n\t<div>\n\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t<strong>表达疑虑</strong><br />\n\t\t\t&nbsp;</div>\n\t</div>\n\t<div>\n\t\t<div>\n\t\t\t<table border="0" cellpadding="0" cellspacing="0" style="width: 90%;" width="700">\n\t\t\t\t<tbody>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t使用类似下面的表达表示疑虑。注意语调的变化如何加深说话人的疑虑程度。&nbsp;&nbsp;<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style="width: 5%;">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/05/24/v/110524/GE_4.6.2.3.2_1_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td style="width: 40%;">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<em>Are you sure about that?</em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t那你确定吗？</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/05/25/v/110525/GE_4.6.2.3.2_2_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<em>If you say so.&nbsp;</em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t既然你这么说。</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t表达疑虑还有一种方法，就是重复或反驳某人刚说的话。再次注意表示疑虑的人的语调。<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/05/26/v/110526/GE_4.6.2.3.2_3_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tA:<em> I&#39;ll probably go to the spa tonight.</em><br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tB: <em><strong>The spa?&nbsp;&nbsp;</strong>&nbsp; </em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t我今晚很可能会去水疗中心？<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t水疗中心？</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\thttps://cns2.ef-cdn.com/Juno/11/05/23/v/110523/GE_4.6.2.3.2_4_v2.mp3</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tA:<em> We&#39;re going to travel through Europe this year.</em><br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\tB:<em> <strong>You&#39;re not going to Asia?</strong></em></td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t我们今年打算环游欧洲。<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t你不打算去亚洲吗？</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t<tr>\n\t\t\t\t\t\t<td colspan="3">\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t<br />\n\t\t\t\t\t\t\t语言点：注意这些表示疑虑的表达的使用方式和对象。比如，跟老板说 **If you say so** 可能不大好！</td>\n\t\t\t\t\t</tr>\n\t\t\t\t</tbody>\n\t\t\t</table>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t\t<p>\n\t\t\t\t&nbsp;</p>\n\t\t</div>\n\t</div>\n</div>\n<p>\n\t&nbsp;</p>',
